window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Even supervillains have lines they dare not cross. If only the same could be said of heroes....</p> <p>For more than two decades, the sight of Doctor Fid's powered armor has struck terror into the hearts of hero and civilian alike. But when a personal tragedy motivates Doctor Fid to investigate a crime, a plot is uncovered so horrific that even he is taken aback. Haunted by painful memories and profound guilt, the veteran supervillain must race against time if he is to have any hope of confronting the approaching threat. Every battle takes its toll...but the stakes are too high for retreat to be an option.</p> <p>Listen to the supervillainous action-thriller that critics have called \"immediately engaging\", \"ridiculously fun\", and \"a solid foundation for a new series!\"</p>"; 
